snippet.title: Celebrities That Tried To Warn Us About James Franco...
snippet.description:
Celebrities That Tried To Warn Us About James Franco...
A very sad trend that has been going on in Hollywood as of late is that certain celebrities are being exposed for their wrongdoings in the present and in the past and people...are acting surprised. Which is both fine...and not fine. You see, when it comes to people like the fans or even the critics who don't know the celebrity personally or in great depth, it makes sense that many of them would be surprised. BUT, when it comes to the celebrities that DO know them...this is a bit harder to swallow. And in fact, in the case of James Franco, some have tried to warn about him for a long time. Allow us to break it down for you. Be sure to like the video and subscribe to the channel!

Click HERE To Enter The GIVEAWAY! https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCbiT0LUIbQj6CQScvWHJeKQ?sub_confirmation=1

And there you have it, everyone! A look at all the celebrities who have tried to warn us about James Franco as well as those who have spoken out about their relationships about him recently. What do you think is going to happen to James Franco now that he has been exposed as a predator and abuser of women? Do you think that he will be outcast from Hollywood as whole?
